{"tid":2354942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶］友邦保險集團(AIA)首席執行官兼總裁的話","createTime":"2021-01-06T00:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T01:09:43.000Z","uid":71652,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae9f5a7e0de8255e3657eb418f613823f0d8526","tid":2354942,"uid":71652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"陸續有金融機構表態支持「港版國安法」。友邦保險集團在官網刊出「集團首席執行官兼總裁的話」，集團首席執行官兼總裁李源祥表示，全力支持維護一國兩制的國家安全法，它將促進香港的和平發展、保障所有香港人的福祉。<br />\n<br />\n李源祥指，集團1919年源於上海，現以香港作為總部，集團植根於此，對香港未來有堅定不移的信心，法治是香港過往多個世代發展的支柱，亦將是香港未來世代繼續發展和繁榮的關鍵。<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-06-17<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才冇留意開唔知但係AIA唔係屬於外資公司，源於上海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問連登仔仲有冇保險&amp;MPF係AIA<br />\nLink係支那01唔po了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇啦垃圾公司，Agent底褲黃都唔幫襯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />決定捐錢俾大陸"},{"pid":"3c426e67374a31590f19cdb1c1f9f3bdc24c951d","tid":2354942,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6935950e76586ab11a32e5e15a4bdfdbc908a18","tid":2354942,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:00:07.000Z","msg":"以前中國業務係上海,之後共產黨打到黎就搬黎香港"},{"pid":"a5cf3bf6d5b75ce36bb593229728dd81a7929b47","tid":2354942,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"a記 不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}